              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 10:26:01 | 1.40 Gb


Offering the ultimate collection of fresh, unmissable beats, 'Toolroom Ibiza 2014 Vol. 2' delivers a unique playlist of leading DJ's & producers dominating the White Isle this season. Jam-packed with 57 summer smashes from Basement Jaxx, Mark Knight, Dusky, MK, Route 94, GotSome, Weiss, Groove Armada, Sasha, Kove, Jay Lumen, Tube & Berger, Harry Romero, Panda, Copy Paste Soul, Tough Love, Riva Starr & many more, plus a selection of brand new exclusive tracks from Da Fresh, Erik Hagleton, DJ Lora & Deep City Groove as well as a handful of recent Toolroom smashes.
